@3016=~Potion of Invisibility~
@3017=~The crutch of shoddy thieves and cowardly adventures, but also a powerful tool in the hands of trained assassins and scouting rangers, these potions are well known across the face of Faerûn. They confer invisibility similar to the second level wizard spell of the same name. Any action other than movement cause termination of the invisible state. Barring that, the effect will last for 5 turns.

