@3024=~Potion of Speed~
@3025=~Useful for that extra mile or a quick escape, these potions are in common usage among scouts and heralds. The affected creature gains +6 to movement speed and can make an extra half attack each round (spellcasting time is not affected). The effects of this potion are not cumulative with themselves or with other similar magic, have a duration of 1 turn, and cannot be dispelled.

