Weight: 1~
@3028=~Violet Potion~
@3029=~This is one of the oddest potions you have ever examined. Once drunk, this mixture causes one's muscles to immediately bulge to completely inhuman proportions, while Dexterity and Constitution are both reduced essentially to that of a slug. The effects last for eight hours, so think carefully before quaffing this suspect drink.

