Weight: 1~
@3032=~Potion of Absorption~
@3033=~There exist terrifying creatures in the wilderness that are a match for even the fiercest Rashemi berserker, so the Witches of Rashemen create these magical flasks to bolster their warriors' resistance. This potion will cushion the user against attacks made against him or her by increasing the imbiber's physical resistance by 25% for a duration of 1 turn. Multiple uses of this potion are not cumulative.

