@3082=~Potion of Memory~
@3083=~Also known as "mage wine", this potion is highly sought after by wizards and bards. When consumed, the magician can immediately bring back into memory two 4th-level or lower spells that have been previously cast. If no spells have been cast yet, then nothing happens. The content is enough for one single dose and the effect is instantaneous.

