@3088=~Potion of Stone Form~
@3089=~The effects experienced after drinking this potion are much like the effects of a Stoneskin spell. The user's skin is partially turned into stone without causing any actual hindrance, protecting them from physical attacks such as melee weapons and projectiles. The first 5 attacks made against the user are stopped, and the skins will disappear thereafter. Multiple uses of this potion are not cumulative. The effect lasts for 5 turns and cannot be dispelled.

